description: Old owners of Swan Nails 1 Inc. submitted refund request for the business license paid 6/6/2016. The business was sold to the new owners, Tracy Trang VO and Trinh T. Ngo on 8/1/2016. The old owners closed the business license acct BU20723210 and were issued a refund check for 9 months totaling $370.18 ($262.54 base tax + $13.58 x 8 employees). Old owners said that new owners paid for their business license, however, no account has been created for this location. Customers may be confused. Please refer customers to BizPort to apply online and get more information.
